name: VesselOfLif3 - Madr3
description:
"Madre" (Mother), my mom is the kindest person I know, she always put others before her self. My mom also have schizophrenia, a thing she battles all of her life. In past two year she in and out mental institution, an episode, a really dark episode, just like when she is younger, when I was just a kid. I LOVE YOU MOM, Get Well Soon.
----------
this is one of my digital drawing series #VesselofLif3, if my work resonate with you, please kindly follow my journey on my twitter/instagram @satrioyudho_p
